name: Recursive Universe Timelapse Prototype
description:
This universe prototype, when played back at an extreme time scale, is shown to follow a perpetual recursive behavior. In this simulation experiment, it seems to grow out of itself.  Made with Trapcode Particular originally posted on [05-05-18]
